<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AudioHub - Premium Audio Equipment</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('header.ejs') %>
    
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-4">About Audio Hub Store</h1>
            <p class="lead mb-5">Your premier destination for premium audio and wearable technology</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="our-story" class="section-padding">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="mb-4">Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Founded in 2025, our mission is to bring the latest in audio and wearable technology to customers who value quality, style, and performance. We believe technology should not only make life easier but also more enjoyable.</p>
                    <p>We specialize in premium headphones, earbuds, speakers, and smartwatches that blend cutting-edge innovation with sleek design. Every product we offer is carefully selected to ensure it meets the highest standards of durability and performance.</p>
                    <p>Our goal is to create a seamless online shopping experience where you can find everything you need to stay connected and entertained. With us, you don’t just buy gadgets—you invest in smarter, more enjoyable living.</p>
                    <a href="/shop" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Shop Our Collection</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607082348824-0a96f2a4b9da?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Our Story" class="img-fluid rounded shadow">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-padding bg-light-custom">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2>Our Product Categories</h2>
                <p class="lead">Discover our range of premium audio and wearable technology</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-headphones product-icon"></i>
                        <h4>Headphones</h4>
                        <p>Experience immersive sound with our collection of over-ear, on-ear, and noise-cancelling headphones.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-volume-up product-icon"></i>
                        <h4>Earbuds</h4>
                        <p>Wireless freedom meets premium sound quality with our selection of true wireless earbuds.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock product-icon"></i>
                        <h4>Smartwatches</h4>
                        <p>Stay connected and track your fitness with our range of feature-packed smartwatches.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm h-100">
                        <i class="fas fa-volume-up product-icon"></i>
                        <h4>Speakers</h4>
                        <p>Fill your space with rich, detailed sound from our portable and home speaker systems.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>



    <%- include('footer.ejs') %>



    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/style.js"></script>
</body>
</html>